{
  "stem": "9898.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mostly-- and we were there-- we kept a place in Aleksandrow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We kept-- we went to Ciechocinek only for the summer, because the people were coming only in the summer there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There we have a little different story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Different-- and I don't how to say [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the beginning of 1930s, my parents moved to [NON-ENGLISH], where that's a big city in Pomerania of 2-- 300,000 people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I was at university.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Interesting to say that, you know, very few young men were taking into the armed services-- Jews-- into the armed services in Poland.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Why they took me, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took me into the officers school, which was not far from Posen, P-O-S-E-N.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was a one-year school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Again, we were only three Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We're all from-- from universities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was from the University of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "One was a history student from Warsaw, and one was from Lvov.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Again-- and the rest-- there were a few hundred of them-- were mostly students of teachers school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It wasn't a university.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They prepared them to be teachers under this-- some lower grades.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now again, I have to say-- not that I want to say something very good about me-- but I was, again, top.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because the three of us, you know, we were all university students.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were top in the-- in to the officers schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And from the officers schools, I was sent to Wloclawek, W-L-O-C-L-A-W-E-K, to the 14th Regiment of Infantry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I was there as a medical officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And all together it was one year, then they let us go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Every few years we had maneuvers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when I was studying in Krakow medicine, I lived in the academic house.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
